    * Update reltool_util

2014-05-06 Michael Truog   <mjtruog at gmail dot com>

    * Cleanup cloudi_service_db_pgsql
        * Move the old epgsql wg driver modules/application/header
          so that its prefix is epgsql_wg
        * Add the semiocast pgsql driver
